\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Welfare-incidence summary for Harvest Commons. The left panel shows cell-level welfare deltas by aggression tercile for \texttt  {hybrid - top\_down\_only}; the larger markers indicate tercile means. The right panel shows the same contrast for targeted agents, reporting both welfare and local patch-health deltas. Relative to top-down-only control, hybrid governance imposes a modest incremental welfare cost while improving local patch health.}}{7}{figure.caption.16}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:harvest_incidence}{{3}{7}{Welfare-incidence summary for Harvest Commons. The left panel shows cell-level welfare deltas by aggression tercile for \texttt {hybrid - top\_down\_only}; the larger markers indicate tercile means. The right panel shows the same contrast for targeted agents, reporting both welfare and local patch-health deltas. Relative to top-down-only control, hybrid governance imposes a modest incremental welfare cost while improving local patch health}{figure.caption.16}{}}
